{
  "text": "As mentioned, the sensor nodes are distributed over the inaccessible environment for observing the ecological modifications based on dynamic temperature, pressure, motions, vibration, pollutants or some other location based predefined or distinctive activities. Here, the deployed sensor nodes are required to send the gathered data to the charging technique is applied to the portable charger, the charger has to be scheduled for recharging the nodes in the considered network. Further, the mobile chargers involve in recharging the sensor batteries and gather information to pass through the nodes based on the predefined route simultaneously [CITATION_1] . This may enhance the network lifetime, but it has some practical complications to execute.",
